#. type: Plain text
#: build/C/man7/boot.7:23
msgid ""
"The B<bootup process> (or \"B<boot sequence>\") varies in details among "
"systems, but can be roughly divided into phases controlled by the following "
"components:"
msgstr ""

#. type: IP
#: build/C/man7/boot.7:23
#, no-wrap
